<node ID="393C2D37-0879-4182-A379-7CF32BC6F153" TEXT="flex-basis" COLOR="#344853" POSITION="right" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#DC2128" WIDTH="6" /><font NAME="HelveticaNeue" SIZE="18" /><node ID="21607DA9-BA0A-4FC8-85D4-FE8A2F84DDCA" TEXT="&#23450;&#20041;&#20102;&#22312;&#20998;&#37197;&#22810;&#20313;&#31354;&#38388;&#20043;&#21069;&#65292;&#39033;&#30446;&#21344;&#25454;&#30340;&#20027;&#36724;&#31354;&#38388;" COLOR="#344853" POSITION="right" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#DC2128" WIDTH="6" /><font NAME="PingFangSC-Regular" SIZE="18" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
<body><p><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 19px "Songti SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "STSongti-SC-Regular"; '>它可以设为跟</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 15px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>width</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 19px "Songti SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "STSongti-SC-Regular"; '>或</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 15px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>height</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 19px "Songti SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "STSongti-SC-Regular"; '>属性一样的值（比如</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 19px "Georgia"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Georgia"; '> 350px</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 19px "Songti SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "STSongti-SC-Regular"; '>），则项目将占据固定空间。</span></p></body>
</html>
