<node ID="FFEFE228-E2FC-454C-83C9-6B2C4BA53D49" TEXT="justify-content" COLOR="#344853" POSITION="left" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#FCB60D" WIDTH="6" /><font NAME="HelveticaNeue" SIZE="18" /><node ID="7BCA3F67-BF17-4116-8D08-05FB6FC5681E" TEXT="&#20027;&#36724;&#19978;&#30340;&#23545;&#40784;&#26041;&#24335;" COLOR="#344853" POSITION="left" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#FCB60D" WIDTH="6" /><font NAME="PingFangSC-Regular" SIZE="18" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
<body><p><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>flex-start</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>（默认值）：左对齐</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>flex-end</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>：右对齐</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>center</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>：</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Monaco"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Monaco"; '> </span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>居中</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>space-between</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>：两端对齐，项目之间的间隔都相等。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>space-around</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>：每个项目两侧的间隔相等。所以，项目之间的间隔比项目与边框的间隔大一倍。</span></p></body>
</html>
</richcontent>
