<node ID="639C9E47-3B27-407D-9BEA-74044BABD975" TEXT="align-items" COLOR="#344853" POSITION="left" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#FCB60D" WIDTH="6" /><font NAME="HelveticaNeue" SIZE="18" /><node ID="706F4893-7503-4A15-A99D-2315F27C180B" TEXT="&#20132;&#21449;&#36724;&#19978;&#30340;&#23545;&#40784;&#26041;&#24335;" COLOR="#344853" POSITION="left" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#FCB60D" WIDTH="6" /><font NAME="PingFangSC-Regular" SIZE="18" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
<body><p><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>flex-start</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>：交叉轴的起点对齐。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>flex-end</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>：交叉轴的终点对齐。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>center</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>：交叉轴的中点对齐。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>baseline</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Monaco"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Monaco"; '>: </span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>项目的第一行文字的基线对齐。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>stretch</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>（默认值）：如果项目未设置高度或设为</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Monaco"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Monaco"; '> auto</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>，将占满整个容器的高度。</span></p></body>
</html>
</richcontent>
