<node ID="8194A5B9-9E62-425F-BED8-39D33414555C" TEXT="align-content" COLOR="#344853" POSITION="left" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#FCB60D" WIDTH="6" /><font NAME="HelveticaNeue" SIZE="18" /><node ID="63CF3241-5C2A-4D41-9210-342852B806D0" TEXT="&#23450;&#20041;&#20102;&#22810;&#26681;&#36724;&#32447;&#30340;&#23545;&#40784;&#26041;&#24335;&#12290;&#22914;&#26524;&#39033;&#30446;&#21482;&#26377;&#19968;&#26681;&#36724;&#32447;&#65292;&#35813;&#23646;&#24615;&#19981;&#36215;&#20316;&#29992;&#12290;" COLOR="#344853" POSITION="left" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#FCB60D" WIDTH="6" /><font NAME="PingFangSC-Regular" SIZE="18" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
<body><p><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>flex-start</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>：与交叉轴的起点对齐。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>flex-end</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>：与交叉轴的终点对齐。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>center</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>：与交叉轴的中点对齐。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>space-between</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>：与交叉轴两端对齐，轴线之间的间隔平均分布。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>space-around</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>：每根轴线两侧的间隔都相等。所以，轴线之间的间隔比轴线与边框的间隔大一倍。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "Courier"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "Courier"; '>stretch</span><span style='color: rgba(14, 14, 14, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>（默认值）：轴线占满整个交叉轴。</span></p></body>
</html>
</richcontent>
